body:
Dug more in history, I see that it was reachable code in https://github.com/golang/go/commit/de8549dfd36bc46ca9c10903dad6e504e1444a86.

But https://github.com/golang/go/commit/e7173dfdfd1c74b1d301da9b6f295ef99b9cc11c removed the only possible case where `status` was being set to `"skip"`, causing it to be unreachable.
